|=== test_doc_comment_tag_section
status = valid
bespon =
  * |```
    |=== key
    (str)> subkey = value
    |```/
  * |```
    |=== key
    (dict)>
    subkey = value
    |```/
  * |```
    |=== key
    (dict)>
    (str)> subkey = value
    |```/
  * |```
    |=== key
    ### doc comment ###
    (dict)>
    ### doc comment ###
    (str)> subkey =
      ### doc comment ###
      value
    |```/
  * |```
    |=== key
    ### doc comment ###
    subkey =
      ### doc comment ###
      value
    |```/
json = `{"key": {"subkey": "value"}}`



